data.description: Welcome to this charming 4-bedroom home set on over half an acre of land. Step into the inviting family room, where a cozy fireplace welcomes you. The living room, family room, and kitchen are bathed in natural light, creating a warm and airy atmosphere. The kitchen boasts ample storage space, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The sizable master bedroom features a master bath with double sinks and a relaxing bathtub with a shower. Three additional roomy bedrooms each come with their own closet space. Outside, a deck awaits at the back, offering an ideal space to entertain friends and family. The spacious open backyard is adorned with plenty of trees, providing a serene and private oasis. Discover the perfect blend of comfort and nature in this delightful home.
